        "jsCode": "const now = new Date();\n\n// yesterday\nconst y = new Date(now);\ny.setDate(now.getDate() - 1);\n\nconst pad = n => n.toString().padStart(2, '0');\n\nconst year = y.getFullYear();\nconst month = pad(y.getMonth() + 1);\nconst day = pad(y.getDate());\n\nconst dateStr = `${year}-${month}-${day}`;\n\n// IST timestamps\nconst start = `${dateStr}T00:00:00+05:30`;\nconst end   = `${dateStr}T23:59:59+05:30`;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    yesterdayDate: dateStr,\n    yesterdayStart: start,\n    yesterdayEnd: end,\n  }\n}];\n"
